<h1 id="sota-guide---green-knob-w4ccm-020">SOTA Guide - Green Knob, W4C/CM-020</h1>

<h4 id="drive-guide---green-knob-w4ccm-020-from-mt-mitchell">Drive Guide - Green Knob (W4C/CM-020) from Mt Mitchell</h4>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Note: This is the Green Knob with a fire tower.  Thereâ€™s another Green Knob which is near Mt Pisgah which has no fire tower.</p>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 0:25, 9.6 miles</li>
  <li><strong>Google Maps</strong> URL from Ashford Dunwoody Rd and I-285 at 33.917, -84.3378:</li>
  <li><strong>Seasonal/Limited Access</strong>: Blue Ridge Parkway closed in bad weather. Check the <a href="http://www.nps.gov/maps/blri/road-closures/">BRP Closure Map</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Directions</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>Head downhill 4.5 miles from parking lot</li>
      <li>L on BRP and go 5.0</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Food</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Last McDonalds:</li>
      <li>Penultimate McDonalds:</li>
      <li>Dinner</li>
    </ul>
