</ul>

<h4 id="drive-guide---green-knob-w4ccm-020-to-atlanta">Drive Guide - Green Knob (W4C/CM-020) TO Atlanta</h4>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 4:05, 230 miles</li>
  <li><strong>Directions</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>L from parking onto BRP and go 38.4</li>
      <li>R on BRP exit and keep R until US-25 (0.1 mile)</li>
      <li>R on US-25 S and go 2.5</li>
      <li>R on NC-146 and go 1.9</li>
      <li>I-26 E and go 16.2</li>
      <li>Exit 54 for US-25 S</li>
      <li>Follow US-25 S to I-85 S</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="trail-guide">Trail Guide</h4>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 0:25, 0.5 miles</li>
  <li><strong>Navigation</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Park at the Green Knob overlook (MM 350.4).</li>
      <li>Walk north on the parkway several hundred yards.</li>
      <li>Take trail on the L. There are 3 major switchbacks on the way up.  When you come to the junction, your are almost to the fire tower; turn left.</li>
      <li>Fire tower on summit.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Trailhead altitude</strong>: ???</li>
  <li><strong>Summit altitude</strong>: ???</li>
  <li><strong>GPS tracks/waypoints</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>Parking: 35.71781,-82.22248</li>
      <li>Leave road: 35.71938,-82.22230</li>
      <li>Summit: 35.7206, -82.2236</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

